::Incarcinator::

Incarcinator felt laser shots dig into him from below, flying 
sideways but not able to avoid the x-ray blast. He growls, his 
systems working on the damage that had been done to his insides from 
the blast. He fires three shells down at Wildrider, and continues 
flying upward.
